PrecisReappointment of PIERRE R. DION, of Ottawa, Ontario, and JOHN RICHARD LISOWSKI, of London, Ontario, as part-time members of the National Parole Board, Ontario Regional Division, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years, effective May 17, 2002.
